1414
01:19:29.490 --> 01:19:33.310
dependency, vulnerability, and unequal power remove

1415
01:19:33.450 --> 01:19:37.110
any genuine freedom of choice. That description

1416
01:19:37.170 --> 01:19:40.310
reflects the reality faced by many family carers in New

1417
01:19:40.390 --> 01:19:41.960
ZealandToday,

1418
01:19:42.860 --> 01:19:45.840
